ivardefs.name: basedOn_
ivardefs.desc: A plan, proposal or order that is fulfilled in whole or in part by this event.

ivardefs.name: destination
ivardefs.desc: Identification of the facility/location where the Supply was shipped to, as part of the dispense event.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Identifier for the supply delivery event that is used to identify it across multiple disparate systems.

ivardefs.name: partOf_
ivardefs.desc: A larger event of which this particular event is a component or step.

ivardefs.name: patient
ivardefs.desc: A link to a resource representing the person whom the delivered item is for.

ivardefs.name: receiver_
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the person who picked up the Supply.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: A code specifying the state of the dispense event.

ivardefs.name: suppliedItem
ivardefs.desc: The item that is being delivered or has been supplied.

ivardefs.name: supplier
ivardefs.desc: The individual responsible for dispensing the medication, supplier or device.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the type of dispensing event that is performed. Examples include: Trial Fill, Completion of Trial, Partial Fill, Emergency Fill, Samples, etc.

properties.desc: Record of delivery of what is supplied.
